---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About GetEVReal" description="About Mike, the GetEVReal mission, social channels, and a contact form for partnerships, questions, and interviews.">
<section><div class="container about-grid"><div class="pull-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553440569-bcc63803a83d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Electric SUV parked in a modern city at dusk" width="1200" height="1400" fetchpriority="high" /></div><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">About the project</p><h2>GetEVReal follows one honest road to a first electric vehicle.</h2><p>Hi! I'm Mike, I'm here to explain why this site exists, and set the expectation that you readers will get transparent research, personal testing notes, and practical takes instead of hype.</p><div class="social-list"><a class="pill" href="https://youtube.com/@getevreal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a><a class="pill" href="https://instagram.com/getevreal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a><a class="pill" href="https://tiktok.com/@getevreal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TikTok</a><a class="pill" href="mailto:mike@getevreal.com">mike@getevreal.com</a></div></div></div></section>
<section><div class="container contact-grid"><div class="card"><p class="eyebrow">What to say here</p><h2 style="font-size:var(--text-xl);margin:.6rem 0 1rem;">Build authority with experience.</h2><p class="muted">I'm going to talk to people, I'm going to go on rides, I'm going to talk to banks managers and auto mechanics. Along the way I'll share things I find value in.</p><div class="cards-3" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem;margin-top:1.5rem;"><div class="card"><h3>Partnerships.</h3><p class="muted">You have something you want to share? A great tip everyone HAS to know .. send it to me and I'll get it out there.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Trust signal.</h3><p class="muted">There will be affiliate links .. which means you buy the same stuff you were going to buy, but I get a little thank you for sending you their way.</p></div></div></div><div class="form-shell" style="padding:var(--space-6);"><p class="eyebrow">Contact Mike</p><h2 style="font-size:var(--text-xl);margin:.6rem 0 1rem;">A simple form wired for email delivery.</h2><form action="https://formsubmit.co/mike@getevreal.com" method="POST"><input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New GetEVReal contact form message" /><input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" /><input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://getevreal.com/about/?sent=1" /><label>Name<input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="name" required /></label><label>Email<input type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required /></label><label>Message<textarea name="message" required></textarea></label><button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send message</button></form><p class="form-note">Replace FormSubmit with Netlify Forms, Basin, Formspree, or Resend + API route later if you want branded success screens and spam filtering.</p></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
